lease_help.en: This is your signed lease agreement. You may download, print, or request notarization.
lease_help.es: Este es su contrato de arrendamiento firmado. Puede descargarlo, imprimirlo o solicitar notarización.
lease_help.som: Tani waa heshiiskaaga kirada ee la saxiixay. Waxaad u soo dejisan kartaa, daabacan kartaa, ama codsan kartaa xaqiijin.
lease_help.hmn: Qhov no yog koj daim ntawv cog lus xauj tsev uas tau kos npe. Koj tuaj yeem rub tawm, luam tawm, lossis thov kom muaj kev lees paub.

eviction_help.en: This is a formal eviction notice. Please review your rights and contact support.
eviction_help.es: Este es un aviso formal de desalojo. Revise sus derechos y comuníquese con el soporte.
eviction_help.som: Tani waa ogeysiis rasmi ah oo ka saarid ah. Fadlan dib u eeg xuquuqdaada oo la xiriir taageerada.
eviction_help.hmn: Qhov no yog ib daim ntawv ceeb toom tshem tawm. Thov xyuas koj cov cai thiab hu rau kev pab.
